            <proc:Code>A</proc:Code>
            <proc:Description>The Defense Media Activity (DMA) Fiscal Year 2021 program of $7.993 million dollars continues to provide capital investment funds for ongoing automation of major equipment and systems initiatives used to execute the media and visual information and overseas radio and television information and joint training and education missions, providing improved storage, management, and distribution of DoD imagery and visual information products.</proc:Description>
            <proc:Justification>The Defense Media Activity (DMA) Fiscal Year 2021 program of $7,993 million dollars will provide capital investment funds for ongoing automation of major equipment and systems initiatives used to execute the media and visual information, overseas radio and television information and joint training and education missions.  

FY21 Program Adjustments:
Defense Wide Review (DWR): American Forces Network (AFN) Reduction of $2,601,000
Fourth Estate Network Optimization Reduction of $576,000</proc:Justification>
